    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. It\u2019s perfect if you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s well-loved and ready for its next adventure. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
