    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust BMW E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example is equipped with a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure chassis rigidity. The suspension geometry remains true, providing the tactile feedback and telepathic turn-in these chassis are renowned for. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its age, the drivetrain is in excellent health with consistent compression across all cylinders. A purist\u2019s driver that is ready for the canyons or the circuit.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
